    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">How does the 50% deductible waiver work?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">When you receive medical treatment outside the United States, your chosen deductible is automatically reduced by 50%. A $2,500 deductible becomes $1,250 for care in Mexico, Portugal, Thailand, etc. The waiver applies per policy period, not per claim.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Why are IMG's Trustpilot reviews so high (4.6/5)?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">IMG has built a strong reputation for affordable pricing, easy enrollment, and generally good customer service. The 19,000+ reviews reflect satisfied customers who value the price-coverage balance. That said, individual experiences with claims vary.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Can I lower my deductible at renewal?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">No. IMG does not allow you to lower your deductible when renewing your policy. You can raise it (to reduce premiums) but not lower it. Choose your initial deductible carefully.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What happens when I turn 75?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">IMG offers automatic transition to the Global Senior Plan with no new underwriting. Your coverage continues without gap. This is a significant benefit—most insurers require new applications at this age, which can be difficult with health conditions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Why is the free look period only 3 days?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">IMG's 3-day free look period is shorter than the industry standard (10-21 days). This means you have less time to cancel for a full refund. Review your policy documents immediately upon receipt.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Does IMG cover adventure sports?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">IMG covers amateur sports but excludes professional athletics and many extreme sports. If you regularly do activities like BASE jumping, heli-skiing, or professional racing, coverage may not apply. Check the policy exclusions for your specific activities.</p>
    </div>
